{"tid":127474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【男人最痛】睇掃黃行動直播新聞 俄男驚見老婆當場被捕","createTime":"2017-02-20T06:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T11:24:25.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42fb2eee2bb9547f87ca57360e8d6f2efe662c57","tid":127474,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T06:25:37.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯一位男士收看新聞報道當局的妓院掃黃行動時，竟見到最熟悉的臉孔－－他的太太。不過太太並非行動的執法人員，而是提供性服務的妓女。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170219/large/1487435505_f893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170219%2Flarge%2F1487435505_f893.jpg&h=8395a617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿萊克謝耶夫（Igor Alexeev）與瑪麗亞（Maria）結婚8年，育有一位6歲女兒。阿萊克謝耶夫在收看新聞直播，簡直不能相信自己的雙眼，他見身穿超低胸吊帶背心、穿黑色絲襪的瑪麗亞坐在床邊梳化，面對執法人員的問話她似是見慣不怪，表現從容不迫，悠然自得地喝茶。瑪麗亞最後被鎖上手銬帶走。<br />\n<br />\n阿萊克謝耶夫在網上一輪搜尋後，才發現枕邊人提供多項性服務，更找到她的賣身價目表，例如過夜一晚盛惠200英鎊（約1,930港元）。<br />\n<br />\n阿萊克謝耶夫已與瑪麗亞分開，並取得6歲女兒的撫養權，他計劃再向法庭申請阻止瑪麗亞探望女兒，聲稱是要避免女兒在親母當妓女的羞恥感及尷尬情況下成長。瑪麗亞則反駁丈夫賺不夠錢養家，沒有資格批評她。警方指瑪麗亞目前面臨多項刑事起訴。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》/《都市報》"},{"pid":"f76bdaff1a8f55d7d92c5b70c4adb91dc851dc57","tid":127474,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4sRFxcCaQPY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4sRFxcCaQPY&d=qB%2BEr1lTQcBPVU2CyFsNogHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=d675ab93\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4sRFxcCaQPY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f448c7f96e0d5cddb732c12065d335d4a04ea9d3","tid":127474,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T06:31:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">瑪麗亞則反駁丈夫賺不夠錢養家，沒有資格批評她。</span><br />\n又真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果夠錢洗 邊個會想做雞? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8926b500f26b89a31dfc8046afa8af1aaeba0809","tid":127474,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">瑪麗亞則反駁丈夫賺不夠錢養家，沒有資格批評她。</span><br />\n又真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果夠錢洗 邊個會想做雞? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b53e270e5711ac67789d01c1a237b671697ac4d","tid":127474,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:16:19.000Z","msg":"咁都值200鎊?"},{"pid":"d28e7959b856ffe20fba330130d8ca5522d0a4d5","tid":127474,"uid":18258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:24:25.000Z","msg":"呀媽係性母瑪麗亞個女應感到光榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}